      "description": "This car is in mint condition. The exterior is free of scratches, dents, and paint imperfections, presenting a clean and uniform finish. The interior shows no signs of wear, with all surfaces, upholstery, and components in like-new condition. Mechanically, the car functions as expected with no known issues.",
